content.webTitle: Subbuteo to rush out dancing Crouch model

fields.headline: Subbuteo to rush out dancing Crouch model
fields.bodyText: Peter Crouch and his robotic dance are to be immortalised in a Subbuteo figure. A spokesman said: "The Crouch bop has really made its way into the public consciousness so it seems like the right thing to do. We are working flat out to get the figure out."
